Extracted from Bottom trawl surveys

The survey biomass indices for the focal species within the mskeyrun project

surveyIndexAll

The survey biomass indices for all species within the mskeyrun project

surveyIndexA4

The survey biomass indices for the focal species within the mskeyrun project from the Albatross IV era

surveyIndexA4All

The survey biomass indices for all species within the mskeyrun project from the Albatross IV era

surveyIndexHB

The survey biomass indices for the focal species within the mskeyrun project from the Bigelow era

surveyIndexHBAll

The survey biomass indices for all species within the mskeyrun project from the Bigelow era

realBiolPar

The focal species biological parameters in mskeyrun project

realSurveyLennumcomp

Survey length composition for the mskeyrun project based on bottom trawl survey data
